com.ibm.cloud.objectstorage.services.s3.internal

Interface S3DirectSpi

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AmazonS3, AmazonS3EncryptionV2
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractAmazonS3, AmazonS3Client, S3Direct

    public interface S3DirectSpi
    A Service Provider Interface that allows direct access to the underlying non-encrypting S3 client of an S3 encryption client instance.
